7
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:45,720
Curiosity, exploration,

8
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:47,440
fascination, destruction,

9
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:48,840
and emotional abuse.

10
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:50,120
I guess

11
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:51,520
Cao Wenwen

12
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:53,520
is currently in the fascination stage.

13
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:56,520
And Su Na should be in the destruction stage,

14
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:59,120
or even possibly emotional abuse.

15
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:04,400
Wu Fei is already dead.

16
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:07,760
How can Cao Wenwen and Su Na still be controlled by him?

17
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:09,840
Death is only the demise of the physical body.

18
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:12,240
But Wu Fei subjected them to mental manipulation.

19
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,680
This is continuous.

20
00:02:15,880 --> 00:02:17,010
Then how do you think

21
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:21,079
this clue is related to Wu Fei's death?

22
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:24,680
I guess

23
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:28,820
someone must have broken free from Wu Fei's manipulation.

24
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,200
After breaking free,

25
00:02:31,440 --> 00:02:33,680
