26
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:34,200
so...

27
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:36,760
The killer is someone deeply hurt by Wu Fei.

28
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:00,240
Zoom in.

29
00:03:05,640 --> 00:03:07,170
Su Na's marks aren't burns.

30
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:08,730
It's self-harm.

31
00:03:13,920 --> 00:03:14,720
I was wrong.

32
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:17,440
I only eat salad every day now.

33
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:19,410
I won't smoke or drink anymore.

34
00:03:19,480 --> 00:03:22,480
Every time I crave a smoke, I punish myself.

35
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:24,640
Please don't leave me again.

36
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:27,520
Without you, what's the point of living?

37
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:28,800
Darling.

38
00:03:29,079 --> 00:03:32,120
In three days it will be our one-year anniversary.

39
00:03:32,320 --> 00:03:34,720
Can you come over and keep me company again?

40
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:39,320
I think we need to end this once and for all.

41
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:41,640
In three days.

42
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:44,720
