43
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:47,200
Oh no. Su Na is suicidal.

44
00:03:50,640 --> 00:03:52,000
You really hit the nail on the head.

45
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:54,130
She's not dead yet. Call an ambulance.

46
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:57,480
Go.

47
00:03:57,480 --> 00:03:57,880
Hurry!

48
00:03:58,120 --> 00:03:59,400
Hello, is this 120?

49
