65
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:42,480
Captain Gu.

66
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,120
Yeah.

67
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:44,040
You look around outside.

68
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:45,700
I'll go inside and take a look.

69
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:51,760
Qiu Chen.

70
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:57,580
Here's a suicide note.

71
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:02,800
Dear family and friends,

72
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:05,240
when you read this letter,

73
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:07,480
I should have already left this world.

74
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,880
This is a suicide note,

75
00:06:10,320 --> 00:06:12,040
and also a confession.

76
00:06:12,960 --> 00:06:13,760
That's right.

77
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:15,400
I killed Wu Fei

78
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:17,420
and made him into a wax figure.

79
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:20,680
I hated him as much as I loved him.

80
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:24,320
Sometimes I wish I had never met him.

81
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:28,680
But sometimes I want to go back to the day we first met.

82
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:32,800
He said it was love at first sight.

83
00:06:33,400 --> 00:06:35,760
He used to say I was a female star,

84
00:06:36,159 --> 00:06:37,560
and that I was perfect.

85
00:06:38,400 --> 00:06:39,860
But after we got together,

86
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:42,570
he started to change me in the name of love,

87
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:42,930
Nana,

88
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:43,980
and control me.

89
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:47,680
Have you gained a little weight recently?

90
00:06:48,080 --> 00:06:51,320
He always says hurtful things in a caring tone,

91
00:06:52,280 --> 00:06:55,280
