92
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:56,540
He always puts me down,

93
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:59,680
and tells me that only he can tolerate me.

94
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:01,600
Gradually,

95
00:07:02,080 --> 00:07:03,880
I became more and more sensitive.

96
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:05,200
Are you really a model?

97
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:08,440
Then I'll just have a salad.

98
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:10,240
Oh, it's okay, Nana.

99
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:11,320
I just want you to be healthy.

100
00:07:11,320 --> 00:07:13,160
Your health is more important than anything.

101
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:15,680
Even if you get fat

102
00:07:15,760 --> 00:07:16,720
or ugly,

103
00:07:16,840 --> 00:07:19,600
even if everyone forgets your former glory,

104
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:20,520
I, Wu Fei,

105
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:25,400
will always remember how you shined on stage.

106
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,400
Baby.

107
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:30,280
I know I have many flaws.

108
00:07:30,840 --> 00:07:33,040
Thank you for always putting up with me.

109
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:38,120
And Nana,

110
00:07:39,960 --> 00:07:41,280
if possible,

111
00:07:41,840 --> 00:07:42,480
could you please

112
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:44,810
stop going out drinking with your friend?

113
00:07:45,400 --> 00:07:47,240
Every time I see you drunk,

114
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:49,480
