115
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:52,200
Can't you just stay home and wait for me?

116
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:55,000
I want to see you the moment I get home.

117
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:57,159
All right.

118
00:07:57,440 --> 00:07:58,500
I won't go anymore.

119
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:00,320
I'll wait for you at home.

120
