What's wrong, Nana?

122
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:08,740
Wu Fei, what exactly is going on between you and Cao Wenwen?

123
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:14,440
Nana, you really misunderstood.

124
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:16,200
Cao Wenwen's family is rich and powerful.

125
00:08:16,200 --> 00:08:18,800
They can bring a lot of resources to the school.

126
00:08:19,400 --> 00:08:21,720
I did all this for you,

127
00:08:22,640 --> 00:08:24,280
