130
00:08:31,760 --> 00:08:33,559
You've really disappointed me.

131
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:37,200
I'm sorry. I shouldn't have lost my temper at you.

132
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,039
I understand you.

133
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:46,020
You need someone to spend more time with you.

134
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:51,400
I failed to do my duty as a boyfriend.

135
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:52,800
We should

136
