137
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:58,680
The repeated breakups

138
00:08:59,080 --> 00:08:59,740
and makeups

139
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:01,650
have left me exhausted.

140
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,970
It seems I'm never good enough,

141
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:06,000
