142
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:10,200
He always manages to make everything my fault.

143
00:09:11,680 --> 00:09:14,160
This suicide note seems pretty convincing.

144
00:09:14,760 --> 00:09:16,000
But I think

145
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:18,480
at most it just proves that Su Na...

146
00:09:18,760 --> 00:09:20,220
She has the motive to kill.

147
00:09:21,760 --> 00:09:23,600
Does she have the ability to do it?

148
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:24,730
Mistake number one.

149
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:26,280
Wu Fei is 1.8 meters tall

150
00:09:26,280 --> 00:09:27,680
