151
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:28,800
Su Na is so thin.

152
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:31,000
It would be hard for her to move his body.

153
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:32,120
But there is one suspicious detail.

154
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:33,120
I found traces of Wu Fei in Su Na's car,

155
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:35,240
