156
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:36,900
But there are no bloodstains.

157
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:39,720
Hey, this is indeed a bit strange.

158
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:43,080
First of all, does Su Na have

159
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:45,680
