163
00:09:50,280 --> 00:09:51,810
Isn't this contradictory?

164
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:53,880
Zhai is finally right.

165
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:57,080
I found this at Su Na's house.

166
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:58,040
Her diary.

167
00:09:59,520 --> 00:10:00,520
Then according to her habits,

168
00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:03,720
