178
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:24,880
If it really was forged,

179
00:10:25,280 --> 00:10:27,880
then that person must be someone in the school,

180
00:10:27,920 --> 00:10:28,580
and someone

181
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:32,080
who knows Wu Fei and Su Na very well.

182
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:36,440
But I think this love letter is written so sincerely,

183
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:37,900
