184
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:39,360
It doesn't seem to be a forgery.

185
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:42,960
What if the murderer was also emotionally manipulated by Wu Fei?

186
00:10:44,840 --> 00:10:46,560
That's not impossible.

187
00:10:48,160 --> 00:10:48,680
Sigh.

188
00:10:48,760 --> 00:10:51,840
Currently, the murder weapon, Wu Fei's ears,

189
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:53,900
