190
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:56,920
Let's do this.

191
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:59,780
Let's go to the hospital and check on Su Na first.

192
00:11:00,400 --> 00:11:00,600
But after we got together, he began to transform and control me in the name of love. He

193
00:11:00,560 --> 00:11:01,200
always spoke hurtful words in a caring tone, intentionally or unintentionally creating anxiety for me.

194
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:05,530
He always put me down, and told me that only he could tolerate me. Gradually...

195
00:11:07,800 --> 00:11:09,760
No, I didn't write this suicide note.

196
00:11:09,760 --> 00:11:10,480
I couldn't have killed anyone.

197
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:11,410
Absolutely not.

198
00:11:11,880 --> 00:11:13,040
Where did this come from?

199
00:11:13,040 --> 00:11:15,040
It was found in a school file folder.

200
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:16,840
The person who left this note

201
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:18,920
must be from inside your school.

202
00:11:18,920 --> 00:11:19,680
And

203
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:21,680
this person knows you

204
00:11:22,040 --> 00:11:24,160
and Wu Fei very well.

205
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:25,170
Su Na,

206
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:27,800
who do you think it is?

207
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:30,960
I don't know.

208
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,160
I have no suspects.

209
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:37,120
Tell us everything you know.

210
00:11:37,920 --> 00:11:40,320
That's the only way we can catch the killer.

211
00:11:46,560 --> 00:11:49,800
Wu Fei also had a secret apartment.

212
00:11:50,880 --> 00:11:52,880
It's in a very remote neighborhood.

213
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:55,360
